@node Main "g77.guide"
@next "Copying"

Introduction
************

This manual documents how to run, install and port @{b}g77@{ub}, as well as its
new features and incompatibilities, and how to report bugs.  It
corresponds to the GCC-3.4.0 version of @{b}g77@{ub}.


 @{" Copying        " link "Copying"}  GNU General Public License says
                    how you can copy and share GNU Fortran.
