This intrinsic is not yet implemented.  The name is, however, reserved
as an intrinsic.  Use @{b}EXTERNAL AdjustL@{ub} to use this name for an external
procedure.

@endnode

@node "AdjustR Intrinsic" "g77.guide/AdjustR Intrinsic"
