And Intrinsic
.............

     And(I, J)

And: @{b}INTEGER@{ub} or @{b}LOGICAL@{ub} function, the exact type being the result of
cross-promoting the types of all the arguments.

I: @{b}INTEGER@{ub} or @{b}LOGICAL@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

J: @{b}INTEGER@{ub} or @{b}LOGICAL@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

Intrinsic groups: @{b}f2c@{ub}.

Description:

   Returns value resulting from boolean AND of pair of bits in each of
I and J.

