CosH: @{b}REAL@{ub} function, the @{b}KIND=@{ub} value of the type being that of argument
X.

X: @{b}REAL@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

Intrinsic groups: (standard FORTRAN 77).

Description:

   Returns the hyperbolic cosine of X.

@endnode

