DTan: @{b}REAL(KIND=2)@{ub} function.

X: @{b}REAL(KIND=2)@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

Intrinsic groups: (standard FORTRAN 77).

Description:

   Archaic form of @{b}TAN()@{ub} that is specific to one type for X.  See
