I: @{b}INTEGER@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

J: @{b}INTEGER@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

Intrinsic groups: @{b}mil@{ub}, @{b}f90@{ub}, @{b}vxt@{ub}.

Description:

   Returns value resulting from boolean exclusive-OR of pair of bits in
each of I and J.

@endnode

@node "IErrNo Intrinsic" "g77.guide/IErrNo Intrinsic"
@next "IFix Intrinsic"
@prev "IEOr Intrinsic"
