IErrNo Intrinsic
................

     IErrNo()

IErrNo: @{b}INTEGER(KIND=1)@{ub} function.

Intrinsic groups: @{b}unix@{ub}.

Description:

   Returns the last system error number (corresponding to the C @{b}errno@{ub}).

@endnode

