@node "MvBits Intrinsic" "g77.guide/MvBits Intrinsic"
@next "Nearest Intrinsic"
@prev "Modulo Intrinsic"
@toc "Table of Intrinsic Functions"

MvBits Intrinsic
................

     CALL MvBits(FROM, FROMPOS, LEN, TO, TOPOS)

FROM: @{b}INTEGER@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

FROMPOS: @{b}INTEGER@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

LEN: @{b}INTEGER@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

TO: @{b}INTEGER@{ub} with same @{b}KIND=@{ub} value as for FROM; scalar; INTENT(INOUT).

TOPOS: @{b}INTEGER@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

Intrinsic groups: @{b}mil@{ub}, @{b}f90@{ub}, @{b}vxt@{ub}.

Description:

   Moves LEN bits from positions FROMPOS through @{b}FROMPOS+LEN-1@{ub} of FROM
to positions TOPOS through @{b}FROMPOS+LEN-1@{ub} of TO.  The portion of argument
TO not affected by the movement of bits is unchanged.  Arguments FROM
and TO are permitted to be the same numeric storage unit.  The values
of @{b}FROMPOS+LEN@{ub} and @{b}TOPOS+LEN@{ub} must be less than or equal to
@{b}BIT_SIZE(FROM)@{ub}.

@endnode

@node "Nearest Intrinsic" "g77.guide/Nearest Intrinsic"
@next "NInt Intrinsic"
@prev "MvBits Intrinsic"
@toc "Table of Intrinsic Functions"

Nearest Intrinsic
.................

This intrinsic is not yet implemented.  The name is, however, reserved
as an intrinsic.  Use @{b}EXTERNAL Nearest@{ub} to use this name for an external
