Sngl: @{b}REAL(KIND=1)@{ub} function.

A: @{b}REAL(KIND=2)@{ub}; scalar; INTENT(IN).

Intrinsic groups: (standard FORTRAN 77).

Description:

   Archaic form of @{b}REAL()@{ub} that is specific to one type for A.  See
@{"Real Intrinsic" link "Real Intrinsic"}.

